Hi amigas/ amigos . Welcome to my Sculpt Haus page. I might look familiar to some of you already from the front desk but with a new career at Sculpt Haus comes the need for a new Instagram presence. 

I’ll start with telling you a little bit of myself. I’m a proud Latina born in Mexico (I’ll probably be your new translator in office). I have been involved in the beauty world with a little of modeling,pageants  and cosmetology school and now here at Sculpt Haus. I’m a Zo certified expert.  And Moxi certified. I’am gradually growing a patient before & after portfolio. And continue my education to further treat you in the treatment room . Thank you in advanced for sticking around. 🫧
